{"id":"e204a5546ca9d976bc76e313417489900d96867be6a0e950b1194286fda8f022","item_id":"835930e55a:0","text":"Analytic Light（解析灯光）"}
{"id":"ea6af439eb85ec65d3aa85e6abf11d8e3ca39650641f79f28559e0736c31767e","item_id":"835930e55a:1","text":"要添加 light（灯光），请选择一种 light tool（灯光工具），例如 Dome"}
{"id":"4f56bf5fd8e4753ba57720268f0333576ac22c9387534579f73848a433d99a1b","item_id":"835930e55a:2","text":"工具，位于"}
{"id":"bcd220fd0366683bd6a92943b39cd21fbf0477f918c1ba7fe724f1316c2cf1a9","item_id":"835930e55a:3","text":"RenderMan Shelf（RenderMan 工具架）中"}
{"id":"7fc31941f17c45d1f3b06ea8b5784beb40d9bc7339151fbad61bed978e90bee3","item_id":"835930e55a:4","text":"，并会自动创建 Pxr light OBJ。"}
{"id":"96a739f0e6f2506174bf1a0e208f98072242ad68fb0bd3b7a7c7ec625ac563e0","item_id":"835930e55a:5","text":"也可以通过 OBJ pane（OBJ 面板）中的 TAB menu（TAB 菜单）添加 light。所有 Pxr lights 都列在 Render TAB Menu 下。"}
{"id":"bac1c5e5b87fb1bae67f69f57f2a8b52f7497fd867fe4f351c39796aaa4bb6df","item_id":"835930e55a:6","text":"Light Transformation（灯光变换）"}
{"id":"e45dd8834e66dd590ea871b228cc2e463cbb4e1d2bfe0fdeb6f7e931bf7ca6a4","item_id":"835930e55a:7","text":"你会注意到某些 light 的 transformation components（变换组件）是隐藏的。这是因为它们不适用于该特定 light type（灯光类型）。"}
{"id":"ceda8e25d4a099eb551415db02baca1a3975a1bd1e40911cee48b6eaf9bea4e0","item_id":"835930e55a:8","text":"Light Name（灯光名称）"}
{"id":"cf2a63375a57a64d79cc85ecb25f6da63e8700487d99eb7ee41cecad7882ebb2","item_id":"835930e55a:9","text":"Transformation（变换）"}
{"id":"bce6ad691d4917ed8e21735ee38c09a3c0cb591bd13de9520c6f7f55f9d4bef9","item_id":"835930e55a:10","text":"PxrRectLight（矩形灯）"}
{"id":"2792bc2839a7ce6d3db9a557f65a334dd4940398bb3e3d06735c6f4153447d07","item_id":"835930e55a:11","text":"平移、缩放和旋转。"}
{"id":"2098ffa4ac05d3f62dad7a01cb5066bbb463b84e5cb2cd9c4364c5bf27fafa8b","item_id":"835930e55a:12","text":"PxrDiskLight（圆盘灯）"}
{"id":"2792bc2839a7ce6d3db9a557f65a334dd4940398bb3e3d06735c6f4153447d07","item_id":"835930e55a:13","text":"平移、缩放和旋转。"}
{"id":"52d7ea5640dedc6b78c114b4b9c95c38e8727f28cd01e63a0982a561cd2d54bf","item_id":"835930e55a:14","text":"PxrSphereLight（球形灯）"}
{"id":"db3469a3e68af3e38ddd991316cbd0fbba2c04bc09f92c6904541a3cbae65634","item_id":"835930e55a:15","text":"平移、"}
{"id":"ef379363dd0cb7be66638cf7f8726872c8f9f6f2b41ad218192c763c062d310a","item_id":"835930e55a:16","text":"uniform（均匀）"}
{"id":"c2253506bf69cb61e7f50bb2c34141370336176fc7ec03730e0315d46e875f6e","item_id":"835930e55a:17","text":"缩放和旋转。即使进行非均匀缩放，渲染时仍会显示为 sphere（球体）。"}
{"id":"b5846f52f46ec6fed4e841c80d768118053bdfbd8f85a4a8432c9414bb08ad95","item_id":"835930e55a:18","text":"PxrCylinderLight（圆柱灯）"}
{"id":"db3469a3e68af3e38ddd991316cbd0fbba2c04bc09f92c6904541a3cbae65634","item_id":"835930e55a:19","text":"平移、"}
{"id":"ef379363dd0cb7be66638cf7f8726872c8f9f6f2b41ad218192c763c062d310a","item_id":"835930e55a:20","text":"uniform（均匀）"}
{"id":"12f11cccc62ad8e1c5d24072098673618a19c523bca2bebb569761906b1d994c","item_id":"835930e55a:21","text":"横截面缩放、长度缩放和旋转。即使进行非均匀缩放，渲染时仍会显示为 sphere（球体）。"}
{"id":"c0eb10eb381af128b5545089127bac4730878814b3f8f90234e161d8bb4fbc3a","item_id":"835930e55a:22","text":"PxrDistantLight（远距灯）"}
{"id":"a3b3f2dbcca9c94549103ae92fe1e3a5766401df476603d04bdfab00a7ecea53","item_id":"835930e55a:23","text":"Rotation only（仅旋转）。"}
{"id":"1212e2ab64a08ec5ced8175eb4e0b702d7cfc550ede4593bd2ead1444ee69a02","item_id":"835930e55a:24","text":"PxrDomeLight（穹顶灯）"}
{"id":"a3b3f2dbcca9c94549103ae92fe1e3a5766401df476603d04bdfab00a7ecea53","item_id":"835930e55a:25","text":"Rotation only（仅旋转）。"}
{"id":"902e1d2a62eb9be4cffa7a5918aa7e9aecd6188f0c9abb1f12534471f681ec4c","item_id":"835930e55a:26","text":"PxrPortalLight（门户灯）"}
{"id":"f8596b251477ad0f63f8d04883b8e97d8737f15c049e41ab0fc4800eed286d3b","item_id":"835930e55a:27","text":"类似 PxrRectLight，但还需要一个外部 coordsys（坐标系）来指定 dome texture（穹顶纹理）本身的 orientation（朝向）。"}
{"id":"ee57ed13ccef28fd60c0100c0f99c44fe40ca7c46ba8d37623a5ddce3072bf7b","item_id":"835930e55a:28","text":"PxrEnvDayLight（环境日光）"}
{"id":"a3b3f2dbcca9c94549103ae92fe1e3a5766401df476603d04bdfab00a7ecea53","item_id":"835930e55a:29","text":"Rotation only（仅旋转）。"}
{"id":"fe5c837bc1312943444e33b94d85912089afbdb83a44af0d9da05c80be4ae58d","item_id":"835930e55a:30","text":"PxrAOVLight（AOV 灯）"}
{"id":"a9daa7582ac3350e37d6382a17f9f6f70483d957a9b5d3e6eac444642c4ac880","item_id":"835930e55a:31","text":"由于它不是设计用于 illuminate（照明）的真实 light，因此没有平移、缩放和旋转。"}
{"id":"e3d7c3206d82073ea835c67ccdb018d4919259a92c482760a39b6fedc296811b","item_id":"835930e55a:32","text":"Portal Light（门户灯）"}
{"id":"b344d80e24a3679999fa964450b34bc24d1578a35509f934c1418b0a20d21a67","item_id":"835930e55a:33","text":"这个"}
{"id":"902e1d2a62eb9be4cffa7a5918aa7e9aecd6188f0c9abb1f12534471f681ec4c","item_id":"835930e55a:34","text":"PxrPortalLight（门户灯）"}
{"id":"33b4196c20b4780149a8d7d6666e8ad5410b5f28610ccfc01d926c220a7a3cad","item_id":"835930e55a:35","text":"是通过一个 “portal”（门户）查看 dome light（穹顶灯）的优化版本。要设置 PxrPortalLight OBJ，需要将 Dome Light 参数指向一个 PxrDomeLight OBJ。一个 dome light 可以拥有多个 portal light 子级。如果希望 portal 继承 dome 的 transform（变换），可以将 portal light parent 到 dome 下（可选）。"}
{"id":"a4b49a58a140610a88c6c62b6e078674177a95a6578f61017b388d026a7de483","item_id":"835930e55a:36","text":"RenderMan for Houdini 将根据以下规则专门处理 portal light："}
{"id":"542a41ebcf94b57bfe78c4eb990ac49d3b03897b41fa53df9bf06cdcb292c775","item_id":"835930e55a:37","text":"如果某个参数不是 portal light 的本地参数，它会继承 parent dome light 上该参数的设置。"}
{"id":"f60ac936ff12aa70e1e1d64469d4b76ef3982941ad4871fae3f9abec99731561","item_id":"835930e55a:38","text":"Intensity Multiplier 会与 parent dome 的 light Intensity 相乘。"}
{"id":"680a09b8e10e725d480815c90302b1ecba1312c616e6dde56ec1296454c3902e","item_id":"835930e55a:39","text":"Color Tint 会与 parent dome 的 Color 相乘。"}
{"id":"908edeceb1885300786647dae5c5434dc386b7cd1aa7d359af628efc0514255b","item_id":"835930e55a:40","text":"它会同时应用 dome 的所有 light filters 以及自身的 light filters。"}
{"id":"f87c75fc344f644e8b91b19d821699f43c02153b98e99bf0ccf66f2e5fb0409e","item_id":"835930e55a:41","text":"Mesh Light（网格灯）"}
{"id":"1f2d4fa5d1cbcfb76abfd67120cd6cc7dcd259e5a574e206aec7c5bcc3a8b96d","item_id":"835930e55a:42","text":"要添加 PxrMeshLight（使用所选 geometry 作为 light source），请选择 mesh light tool"}
{"id":"4f56bf5fd8e4753ba57720268f0333576ac22c9387534579f73848a433d99a1b","item_id":"835930e55a:43","text":"工具，位于"}
{"id":"92f336120242e4ed60107fe74166ebc43683a23ef17a2d39d15bd57cdc406b67","item_id":"835930e55a:44","text":"RenderMan Shelf（RenderMan 工具架）"}
{"id":"282027e03bbb2833725fc3932c6f260c4136e4363d0162405d2ee51bb2235eaa","item_id":"835930e55a:45","text":"。此工具会要求你为 mesh light 选择一个对象。这对于创建拉伸霓虹灯或使用圆柱体制作 fluorescent lighting（荧光照明）等效果很有用。shelf tool 会自动填充"}
{"id":"ba414267b3668228a61a7930b79b880ac967edb7ddcad614c2445dc0bdfadb26","item_id":"835930e55a:46","text":"Light Geometry（灯光几何）"}
{"id":"5168dbe6f8c42756441f4f14fdc142e0823659a32990ab4b941cb38fb0ec1722","item_id":"835930e55a:47","text":"参数，也可以手动设置。"}
{"id":"48d2f6f60701d5ba216422a9a19b8b53690eca3d688c96efb8b2e028f4633d42","item_id":"835930e55a:48","text":"Light Attributes（灯光属性）"}
{"id":"9bf83f76455ad4aef72e78b0fb9ba2506e5eaa688dcc264e9ded5a6baba34209","item_id":"835930e55a:49","text":"下面显示 light 的默认属性。Camera visibility（摄影机可见性）默认关闭，便于在 camera（摄影机）前方放置灯光时进行美术指导。"}
{"id":"dae5bbba2baa9ee010cee15075ddd909b60c6cedbd5ea7f568ec5366c340a19f","item_id":"835930e55a:50","text":"Camera Visibility（摄影机可见性） - 使 light 对 camera rays（摄影机光线）可见。"}
{"id":"99f19231dad12fbdfc8435fe419a94f02f07b108b3ff972f7f0ba49ca8b791ba","item_id":"835930e55a:51","text":"Transmission Visibility（透射可见性） - 使 light 在 transmission/refraction（透射/折射）中可见。"}
{"id":"82b7bea657efffd859709a04aabd7745752649617581f843e86f2d000c4f8b06","item_id":"835930e55a:52","text":"Indirect Visibility（间接可见性） - 使 light 对 indirect specular reflections（间接镜面反射）可见。"}
